{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Gundam Malang, Tempat Kumpulnya Perakit Gundam Jawa Timur","content":"<p>Para penyuka <em>pop culture</em> nggak hanya ditemukan di kota besar saja, namun tersebar di berbagai daerah dan kota kecil seluruh Indonesia. Biasanya para fans membentuk komunitas regional yang ternyata sangat solid dan inspiratif. Salah satunya adalah komunitas Gundam Malang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45080\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45080\" data-attachment-id=\"45080\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/01-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45080\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"01-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45080\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Saya berkesempatan untuk menyaksikan <em>event</em> Gundama Challenge 3.0 yang diadakan oleh Gundama, singkatan dari Gundam Malang, dalam acara <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nostalgia-anime-daisuki-japan-festival-2018/\">Daisuki Japan Festival 2018</a> di UMM Dome minggu lalu. Di sana berjejer ratusan model Gundam yang nggak cuma sebatas dirakit, tapi juga dipoles dan dimodifikasi sehingga nggak kelihatan kayak Gundam biasa.</p>\n<p>Hasil karya yang ditampilkan ternyata sangat memukau. Kualitas hingga detilnya mampu menyaingi karya-karya buatan perakit Gundam dari kota besar hingga luar negeri. Apalagi dengan fakta bahwa para pesertanya berasal dari sekitar Malang dan Jawa Timur, patut diapresiasi. Bahkan di daerah sekalipun, ada peminat dan perakit Gundam berbakat.</p>\n<p>Untuk lebih jelasnya, saya mewawancarai Edwin Dewanto, ketua dari komunitas Gundam Malang. Edwin berbaik hati membagikan cerita-cerita tentang Gundam Malang dan kompetisi Gundama Challenge ini. Yuk kita simak bersama!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45081\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45081\" data-attachment-id=\"45081\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/02-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45081\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"02-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45081\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>ME: Bisa dijelakan komunitas apakah Gundama ini?<br />\n</strong>ED: Gundama ini adalah komunitas yang mengakomodir hobi Gundam. Jadi, Gundam itu awalnya dari <em>anime</em> tetapi ada pula <em>action figure</em>-nya, sebuah <em>model kit</em> yang banyak disukai. Mengingat ada banyak teman-teman (di Malang) yang menyukai Gundam, akhirnya terkumpul menjadi satu komunitas.</p>\n<p><strong>ME: Lalu apa sih acara Gundama Challenge?<br />\n</strong>ED: Acara ini adalah kegiatan tahunan kita. Setiap tahun kita mengadakan lomba, kompetisi <em>build</em> (merakit) Gundam. Gundam ini bisa dikatakan sebagai seni, jadi di sini kita mempertandingkan kesenian merakit Gundam.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45082\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45082\" data-attachment-id=\"45082\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/03-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45082 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"03 gundam malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45082\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>ME: Apa saja yang dipertandingkan di Gundama Challenge?<br />\n</strong>ED: Ada tiga kategori: pertama <em>Clean Build</em>, kedua <em>Repaint</em>, ketiga <em>Custom</em>. <em>Clean Build</em> ini maksudnya merakit Gundam biasa sebersih mungkin. Kalau <em>Repaint</em>, Gundam-nya dirakit kemudian dicat ulang. Yang <em>Custom</em> berarti setelah dirakit kemudian Gundam dimodifikai sedemikian rupa dengan tema tertentu supaya membentuk sebuah bentuk Gundam baru.</p>\n<p><strong>ME: Seperti apa kriteria penilaiannya?<br />\n</strong>ED: Rata-rata dari kerapihan, tema, pose, kemudian dan detil modifikasi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45083\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45083\" data-attachment-id=\"45083\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/04-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45083\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"04-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45083\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>ME: Seperti apa tanggapan peserta di tahun ini?<br />\n</strong>ED: Lebih dari target. Jumlah pendaftar meningkat 20% dari tahun sebelumnya.</p>\n<p><strong>ME: Lalu bagaimana dengan kualitas rakitan peserta tahun ini?<br />\n</strong>ED: Kalau dibandingkan dengan tahun lalu, dari kuantitas cukup sama tapi kualitasnya jauh lebih bagus dari lomba tahun sebelumnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45084\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45084\" data-attachment-id=\"45084\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/05-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45084\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"05-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45084\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>ME: Para peserta datang dari Malang atau ada juga dari luar kota?<br />\n</strong>ED: Sebenarnya lomba ini se-Jawa Timur. Ada dari Malang, Kediri, Surabaya, Jombang, Madiun, dan Gresik.</p>\n<p><strong>ME: Selain Gundama Challenge, apa saja aktivitas yang dilakukan komunitas Gundama?<br />\n</strong>ED: Setiap bulan kita mengadakan <em>gathering</em>, setiap hari Minggu di minggu ke-2. Kita kumpul-kumpul, <em>sharing</em>, kemudian membahas masalah Gundam, jual beli, dan segala macam. Yang penting kita berkumpul dan silaturahmi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45085\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45085\" data-attachment-id=\"45085\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/06-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45085\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"06-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45085\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>ME: Selain Gundama Challenge, apakah Gundama memiliki project lainnya?<br />\n</strong>ED: Biasanya kita ikutan <em>event-event</em> Jejepangan, lalu <em>event</em> lain seperti jalan-jalan di <em>car free day</em>. Lalu jika ada bencana alam, kita menggalang dana bareng-bareng. Selebihnya, kita ada jadwal satu tahun rutin mengadakan Gundama Challenge.</p>\n<p><strong>ME: Bagaimana kesan-kesan Gundama selama mengikuti Daisuki Japan Fest?<br />\n</strong>ED: Karena partisipannya dari seluruh Jawa Timur, (acara ini) jadi kesempatan kita untuk meningkatkan animo terhadap Gundam, mengenakan komunitas Gundama supaya lebih besar, serta menyajikan sebuah atraksi lomba yang dapat memberikan kesan kepada pengunjung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45086\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45086\" data-attachment-id=\"45086\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gundam-malang-perakit-gundam-jawa-timur/attachment/07-gundam-malang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-gundam-malang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45086\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang.jpg\" alt=\"07-gundam-malang\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-gundam-malang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45086\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Itu dia wawancara CIAYO Blog dengan komunitas Gundam Malang. Kalau kamu penasaran, kamu bisa cek akun Instagram mereka di @gundammalang. Kamu juga bisa bergabung di grup Facebook mereka di <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/gundamalang/\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/gundamalang/</a>. Terus sukses bagi komunitas Gundama Malang!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"2fb5d499-657d-5abf-8422-8b762c0b80c4"}}}